  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Cesarean section with regional anesthesia, regardless of gestational age.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of magnesium sulphate

          -  General anesthesia

          -  Pre gestational or gestational diabetes

          -  Bowel injury during surgery
      </textblock>
